BT 1 0 0 1 0 65 Tm -0.136316 Tw 15 TL /F2 10 Tf .039216 .039216 .039216 rg (How to use each Module:) Tj /F1 10 Tf ( Each module contains five scripts \227 one per week. Run the script at the opening) Tj T* 0 Tw .7585 Tw (or close of class \(3\2265 minutes\). The module then rotates: Month 1 is Breath, Month 2 is Body, Month 3 is) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.0325 Tw (Mind, Month 4 is Spirit. At Month 5, you return to Breath \227 but your students will go deeper because they've) Tj T* 0 Tw .0905 Tw (been through the cycle. New students can join at any point and still get the full value of whichever module is) Tj T* 0 Tw (current.) Tj T* ET
