BT 1 0 0 1 18 50 Tm /F3 10 Tf 15 TL .055263 Tw (Think about it like this: When you throw a punch, if you overextend your arm, you lose your balance and) Tj T* 0 Tw .159412 Tw (leave yourself open to a counterattack. Our minds do the same thing. When we get angry, frustrated, or) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.854 Tw (distracted, our minds overextend. We lose our 'mental center.' We stop paying attention to what is) Tj T* 0 Tw (happening right here, right now. And in a fight, or in life, that's when we get hit, hurt, or worse.) Tj T* ET
